      <div class="card border-success">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h2 class="m-0">Success</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p>
  Project Pals was able to re-launch their tech with great success. Application latency was reduced by 93%. 
  No matter what country you’re in, every action felt snappy and smooth. Bugs and errors were drastically reduced. 
  Students speaking any language were able to participate in all projects. Finally, and most importantly, 
  <b>customer churn rate was reduced by 70%</b>. Now people not only love the idea of Project Pals, they love the experience!
</p>

